{"_id":"rUUp9ojD6jDjHxCv","name":"The Sorcerer’s Apprentice","permission":{"default":0,"ZhC8ATjW2zJWoMct":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>The Sorcerer&rsquo;s Apprentice</p>\n<p>When y ou pass on your Magical Soul to a willing recipient, they lose any other levels and moves and become a Sorcerer at level 1, with your tags and actions for your Magical Soul.</p>\n<p>You also lose your Sorcerer moves and levels, and may pick a new class.</p>","choices":"","moveType":"advanced","rollFormula":"","moveResults":{"failure":{"value":""},"partial":{"value":""},"success":{"value":""}},"class":"The Sorcerer","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"","moveGroup":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
